data.description: Located in Sparta city limits and minutes from downtown, this home features a functional footprint, oversized double lot, and a finished secondary detached apartment. Welcomed by floor to ceiling windows, bask in the abundance of natural sunlight gleaming over the open living spaces. Cozy up around the stone fireplace, entertain at the large dining table, stay organized with the convenient butler's pantry, and take advantage of the relaxing sauna in the spare bath - there is no shortage of space and attention to details! The detached garage is a great addition for storage, with an accessible half bath. The upper level features a finished apartment featuring a full kitchen, living space, bedroom, and full bath - overlook the backyard firepit from the enclosed sunroom!
